comments:
I get the following stack trace on save sometimes in eclipse.  Once it happens I
can no longer save files until I restart eclipse.
It usually happens when I edit a java file that is in a non-wtp project depended
on by the wtp project, whose jar has been copied to the wtp's project
WEB-INF/lib.  I know it definately happens when the server is running in debug,
and I do the save, but it could be happening at other times too.

I'm on eclipse 3.1M6 (also happens on M5), wtp1.0M3, tomcat 4.1.31 on linux
fedora core 2
